<h1 class='property-title'>overflow-x</h1>
<p class='property-description'>The <code>overflow-x </code><a title="CSS" rel="internal" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en/CSS">CSS</a> property specifies whether to clip content, render a scroll bar or display overflow content of a block-level element, when it overflows at the left and right edges.</p>